77245ab431fb"],

Cell["\<\
The disjoint  diagrams at second order are 5,472 in total. These are \
distributed as follows:
i) 768 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the antidiagonal;
ii) 768 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the diagonal;
iii) 288 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in both the diagonal and the antidiagonal;
iv) 768 Direct diagrams dressed in the left propagator;
v) 768 Direct diagrams dressed in the right propagator;
vi) 288 Direct diagrams dressed in both the left and the right propagator;
vii) 768 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator above;
viii) 768 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator below;
ix) 288 Exchange diagrams dressed in both the above and below propagator;\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8746447846491413`*^9, 3.874644822571206*^9}, {
   3.874644938314557*^9, 3.874644942272763*^9}, {3.8836802941172266`*^9, 
